<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Altadore </h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Located just west of the Elbow River and minutes away from Downtown, is the quiet and
                idyllic residential neighborhood called Altadore in Southwest Calgary. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">Touted as one of the best communities for settling in with a family, Altadore lies between
                the Crowchild Trail and the 14 Street.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The Altadore Real Estate was established in 1945 and comprises of a variety of housing
                options including single family detached homes, townhouses, and apartment condominiums as well.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">With a population of around 8900, Altadore has recently witnessed an influx of high-income
                working professionals, giving rise to the development of luxury townhouses and modern condominiums
                within the community that is regularly listed at an average price of $990,000.</p>

        </div>
